System temperature for sensor-1:
    Sensor Id: 0
    Description: inlet temperature
    Temperature: 25 C      (normal)
System temperature for sensor-2:
    Sensor Id: 1
    Description: outlet temperature
    Temperature: 30 C      (normal)
System temperature for sensor-3:
    Sensor Id: 2
    Description: CPU temperature
    Temperature: 40 C      (high)
textfsm_template:
Value SENSOR_ID (\d+)
Value DESCRIPTION (.*)
Value TEMPERATURE (\d+)
Value STATUS (normal|high)

Start
  ^System\s+temperature\s+for\s+sensor-\d+:$$
  ^\s+Sensor\s+Id:\s+${SENSOR_ID}$$
  ^\s+Description:\s+${DESCRIPTION}$$
  ^\s+Temperature:\s+${TEMPERATURE}\s+C\s+\(${STATUS}\)$$ -> Record
